description: A front-end React-like component file for a Tic Tac Toe game built with Qwik framework, including game logic, UI components, icons, and styles.

methods.name: checkWinner
methods.description: Determines if there is a winner on the current board based on predefined winning line combinations.

methods.name: isBoardFull
methods.description: Checks if all cells in the board are filled, indicating a draw if no winner.

methods.name: cellButtonStyle
methods.description: Generates inline CSS styles for each game cell button based on whether it is disabled or active.
